{"title_page": "Visa requirements for Mauritian citizens", "text_new": "{{distinguish|Visa requirements for Mauritanian citizens}}\n'''Visa requirements for Mauritian citizens''' are administrative entry restrictions by the authorities of other states placed on citizens of [[Mauritius]]. As of 7 April 2020, Mauritian citizens had visa-free or visa on arrival access to 148 countries and territories, ranking the [[Mauritian passport]] 32nd overall and 2nd in Africa in terms of travel freedom according to the [[Visa (document)#Visa restrictions|Henley Passport Index]].<ref>{{cite web |title=The ''Henley Passport Index'' |url=https://www.henleypassportindex.com/assets/2020/Q2/HENLEY_PASSPORT_INDEX_2020_Q2_INFOGRAPHIC_GLOBAL_RANKING_200407.pdf|publisher=Henley & Partners Holdings Ltd |quote=This graph shows the full Global Ranking of the 2020 Henley Passport Index. As the index uses [[Ranking#Dense ranking (\"1223\" ranking)|dense ranking]], in certain cases, a rank is shared by multiple countries because these countries all have the same level of visa-free or visa-on-arrival access.}}</ref> As of April 2019, [[Brunei]], [[Grenada]], [[Seychelles]] and [[Mauritius]] are the only countries whose citizens may travel without a visa to [[China]], [[Russia]], [[Schengen Area]] and the [[United Kingdom]].\n\n==Visa requirements map==\n[[File:Visa requirements for Mauritian citizens.png|800px|thumbnail|center|Visa requirements for Mauritian citizens{{legend|#ed1c24|Mauritius}}{{legend|#22b14c|Visa free access}}{{legend|#b5e61d|Visa on arrival}}{{legend|#61c09a|eVisa}}{{legend|#79D343|Visa available both on arrival or online}}{{legend|lightgrey|Visa required}}]]\n\n== Visa requirements ==\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=\"18%\"| Country\n! width=\"22%\"| Visa requirement\n! Allowed stay\n! Notes (excluding departure fees)\n|-\n| {{flag|Afghanistan}}\n| {{no|Visa required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=MU|destination=AF}}</ref>\n|\n| \n|-\n| {{flag|Albania}}\n| {{yes