ex. As the index uses [[Ranking#Dense ranking (\"1223\" ranking)|dense ranking]], in certain cases, a rank is shared by multiple countries because these countries all have the same level of visa-free or visa-on-arrival access.}}</ref> As of April 2019, [[Brunei]], [[Grenada]], [[Seychelles]] and [[Mauritius]] are the only countries whose citizens may travel without a visa to [[China]], [[Russia]], [[Schengen Area]] and the [[United Kingdom]].\n\n==Visa requirements map==\n[[File:Visa requirements for Mauritian citizens.png|800px|thumbnail|center|Visa requirements for Mauritian citizens{{legend|#ed1c24|Mauritius}}{{legend|#22b14c|Visa free access}}{{legend|#b5e61d|Visa on arrival}}{{legend|#61c09a|eVisa}}{{legend|#79D343|Visa available both on arrival or online}}{{legend|lightgrey|Visa required}}]]\n\n== Visa requirements ==\n\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=\"18%\"| Country\n! width=\"22%\"| Visa requirement\n! Allowed stay\n! Notes (excluding departure fees)\n|-\n| {{flag|Afghanistan}}\n| {{no|Visa required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=MU|destination=AF}}</ref>\n|\n| \n|-\n| {{flag|Albania}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=MU|destination=AL|accessdate=3 August 2014}}</ref>\n| 90 days\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Algeria}}\n| {{no|Visa required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=MU|destination=DZ|accessdate=3 August 2014}}</ref>\n| \n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Andorra}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=MU|destination=AD|accessdate=3 August 2014}}</ref>\n|\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Angola}}\n| {{yes|Visa not required}}<ref>{{Timatic|nationality=MU|destination=AO|accessdate=3 August 2014}}</ref>\n| 30 days\n| \n*For a maximum total stay of 90 days within year period.<ref>[https://mobile.twitter.com/_Muskana/status/964815820898611200]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://angola.topnews.cloud/five-more-visa-free-countries-for-angola-and-35-with-simplified-process/amp/ |title=Archived copy |access-date=2018-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20